http://www.cpac.org:80/sbsc/memo0895.html 204.71.237.74 19970108172715 text/html 4249
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 17:27:23 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Sep-96 19:06:48 GMT
