FUEL VERSUS GASOLINE<BR>
</FONT></B></CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=1>
<TR><TD WIDTH=108></TD><TD WIDTH=120><CENTER><B><FONT FACE="Arial">Fuel Taxes</FONT></B></CENTER>
