</TD><TD WIDTH=80><CENTER><FONT SIZE=1 FACE="Arial">37.9</FONT></CENTER>
</TD><TD WIDTH=90><CENTER><FONT SIZE=1 FACE="Arial">63.4</FONT></CENTER>
