<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H4>Jonathan Wells has received two doctorates, one in Molecular and Cell
Biology from the University of California, Berkeley and one in Religious
Studies from Yale University. Currently he is a post-doctoral research biologist
at the University of California, Berkeley and has taught biology at California
State University, Hayward. Dr. Wells has published technical articles in
both scientific and religious journals, and is author of the book <I>Charles
Hodge's Critique of Darwinism</I> (1988).</H4>
