<title>Application for membership</title>
<h3>Apply for membership ID</h3>

<h5><a href="/townhall/apply.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>



You can apply for a Member ID by 
completing the form below. There is <b>no charge</b> for membership,
but we do ask you to complete the form.
You must complete all the fields
for your application to be accepted. We collect this information so
we have accurate information on who our members are, and thus we are
able to provide services of interest to our members.
<p>
<b>AOL</b> users, please read 

<a href="/townhall/aol.html.cgi/textonly">this</a>



note.
<p>
<b><font size="+3">Please read

<a href="/townhall/email.html.cgi/textonly">these</a>



notes about e-mail addresses.</font></b>
<p>
If you have any technical questions about the application form, please e-mail to
<a href="mailto:applications@townhall.com">applications@townhall.com</a>. Please include your member ID, if you have one, in any message regarding technical difficulties or problems with passwords.<p>

