http://www.cpac.org:80/savers/library/3.html 204.71.237.74 19970108113034 text/html 3696
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 11:30:52 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Mar-96 17:47:31 GMT
