http://www.cpac.org:80/empower/speech01.html 204.71.237.74 19970108102310 text/html 21594
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 10:23:28 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 16-Aug-96 13:32:26 GMT
