http://www.cpac.org:80/discovery/goldinq.html 204.71.237.74 19970109175218 text/html 31313
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 17:52:29 GMT
