You won't hear students reading about dick and Jane at Marva Collins' 
west side preparatory school in Chicago. Even for the little ones, it's 
back to the basics and the classics.  Cleopatra and Mary queen of Scots 
are all stories of very strong women. The classics to me is a real world, 
