over the children. At other schools, teachers, they didn't care. I've had 
teachers tell me, you know, "I'm here to get my paycheck. I don't care if 
you get this or not." While some educators have been critical of her 
teaching methods, students do not share their skepticism. She's a fun 
teacher.
